name: Whiskey Rockers - Set of 2
description:
These clear and stemless whiskey glasses rock - literally!

Pour out the whiskey in the jar and breathe in the aroma - watching your tipple swirl back and forth inside your rocker of choice.

Ideal for ships, these rockers effortlessly counteract the rocking motion of the seas.

Then for drinking fun on dry land, spin or shake your rockers to beat bar boredom - be sure not to spill!

Specifications:

Glass Colour - Clear
Glass Volume - 320ml 
Glass Dimensions - 8x6.5x6.5cm
Glass Weight - 76g
Glass Material - Pressed Soda Glass

Each set contains two rockers. Items dishwasher safe.

name: Wall Mount Bottle Opener
description:
With its pitted chromed finish and bright red slogan, this bottle opener makes a fun addition to any kitchen, bar area or garden wall.

To use, wedge the lid of your bottle under the lip and lift up.
 
The bottle opener effortlessly removes both 'twist off' and regular bottle caps. 

Made from heavy cast zinc with bright red 'OPEN HERE' instructions. 

Wall mounting screws and plugs are included.
